Adult.description: Tropical Kingbirds have a yellowish breast while Cassin's Kingbirds have a dark gray breast. They also have an entirely brown tail while the tail on Cassin's is tipped in white.

Adult/immature.description: Western Kingbirds have a paler gray breast than Cassin's Kingbirds. In flight Western Kingbirds have white outer tail feathers while Cassin's Kingbirds have white on the tip of the tail.
Couch's Kingbirds have yellower chest and no white in tail while Cassin's Kingbirds have a grayer chest and a white-tipped tail.
